"""
Letter Engine v2 — Rebuilt to match locked architecture (CLAUDE.md)

Rules enforced:
1. One consolidated letter per recipient per item (no variant stacking)
2. Recipient routing: bureau letters (FCRA) vs collector letters (FDCPA) — never mixed
3. Content sourced ONLY from consumer-affirmed grounds — no template assertions
4. Math-first structure: audit data → discrepancies → consumer position → requests → law
5. No AE branding, no customer numbers, no generator strings in output
6. Honest position: "I cannot verify" when uncertain, "this is fraud" only when consumer affirmed fraud
"""

from datetime import datetime


